<section>
  <div>
    <h1>Create Task</h1>
    <div class="two-column-row">
      <div>
        <%= render partial: "form" %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <dl>
          <dt>Fun Factor</dt>
          <dd>Tasks that are more fun to do gain less points. This is to encourage people to do tasks that may not be the most desirable to do.</dd>

          <dt>Difficulty</dt>
          <dd>A rough rating of how the hard the task is. It could be based upon skills involved or having to interact with a lot of people etc.</dd>

          <dt>Size</dt>
          <dd>A rough estimation of how long it should take.</dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
